Document: NavigationServer3D
Path: godot/classes/class_navigationserver3d.rst
Summary: A server that manages all 3D navigation-related resources, including maps, regions, agents, and pathfinding queries.

Inherits: Object

NavigationServer3D is the server that manages all 3D navigation-related resources. It can create and update navigation maps, navigation regions, and navigation agents. It also handles pathfinding queries.

It is a singleton, so you can access it from anywhere using `NavigationServer3D.get_singleton()` in GDScript or `NavigationServer3D.Singleton` in C#.

The NavigationServer3D is low-level. For a higher-level API, see NavigationRegion3D and NavigationAgent3D.
---CHUNK---
